high_descs: Go forward, turn left after passing the fridge, go forward to the counter with the wine bottle.
Take the knife in front of the wine bottle from the counter.
Turn around, go forward to the fridge, turn left, go forward to the counter to the right of the sink.
Cut the tomato on the counter into slices.
Put the knife on the counter.
Take a slice of tomato from the counter.
Turn around, go forward, turn left at the fridge.
Chill the tomato on the upper shelf of the fridge. Take the tomato from the fridge.
Turn left go forward, turn right to face the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold slice of tomato in a microwave.

high_descs: Go forward, turn left and go to the counter
Pick up the knife on the counter
Turn around, go forward, turn left
Slice the tomato on the counter
Put the knife on the counter
Pick up a slice of tomato from the counter
Turn around, go forward, turn left at the fridge
Put the slice of tomato in the fridge, wait, pick up the slice of tomato from the fridge
Turn left, go forward, turn right at the microwave
Put the tomato slice in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Cool a slice of tomato and put it into the microwave

high_descs: Go forward to the sink, hang a left, go to the counter where the bottle of wine is.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the counter in front of the bottle of wine.
Turn around, go to the fridge, hang a left and go to the counter where the tomato is.
Cut the tomato into slices.
Put the knife down on the counter in front of the salt.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the counter.
Turn around, go forward to the fridge that is on the left.
Put the tomato inside the fridge and close the door, then remove the cold tomato from the fridge.
Hang a left, go forward to the microwave that is on the right.
Put the tomato inside the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold slice of tomato inside a microwave.
